https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhumas.sorongkota%2Fposts%2F866064986830959&title=PENUTUPAN%20SEMINAR%20SEKALIGUS%20PENGUMUMAN%20PEMENANG%20PAMERAN%20INOVASI%20PELAYANAN%20PUBLIK%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3D%3DPenutupan%20acara%20seminar%20dan%20Simposium%20Reformasi%20Birokrasi%20serta%20Inovasi%20Publik%20tingkat%20Provinsi%20Papua%20Barat%2C%20ditutup%20secara%20resmi%20oleh%20Asisten%20III%20bidang%20Administrasi%20Umum%20Setda%20Kota%20Sorong%2820%2F07%29.%20Bertempat%20di%20halaman%20kantor%20Walikota%20Sorong%2C%20turut%20hadir%20dalam%20acara%20tersebut%20Asisten%20III%20setda%20Provinsi%20Papua%20Barat%2C%20dan%20para%20pejabat%20Kabupaten%2FKota.Dalam%20laporan%20Kepala%20Biro%20Organisasi%20Setda%20Provinsi%20Papua%20Barat%2C%20Supriatna%20Djalimun%2C%20SH%2C%20M.Si%20mengucapkan%20terima%20kasih%20kepada%20Pemerintah%20Daerah%20Kota%20Sorong%20sebagai%20tuan%20rumah%20dan%20kepada%20seluruh%20Pemerintah%20Kabupaten%20se-Provinsi%20Papua%20Barat%20yang%20telah%20ikut%20serta%20dalam%20pameran%20Inovasi%20Pelayanan%20Publik.%20Sambutan%20Walikota%20Sorong%20yang%20dibacakan%20oleh%20Asisten%20III%20Setda%20Kota%20Sorong%2C%20Drs.%20Wilhemus%20Asmuruf%20menyampaikan%20bahwa%20penyelenggaraan%20pemerintahan%20dibutuhkan%20aparatur%20yang%20berkompeten%20dalam%20menjalankan%20birokrasi%2C%20oleh%20sebab%20itu%20Pemerintah%20Daerah%20Kota%20Sorong%20mengharapkan%20seminar%20reformasi%20birokrasi%20serta%20inovasi%20pelayanan%20publik%20seperti%20ini%20perlu%20ditingkatkan%20dan%20disosialisasikan%20pada%20instansi%20pemerintah%20daerah%20di%20Provinsi%20Papua%20Barat%2C%20sehingga%20dapat%20tercipta%20SDM%20Aparatur%20Sipil%20Negara%20yang%20baik%20dari%20segi%20kualitas%2C%20dengan%20tujuan%20terbangunnya%20birokrasi%20yang%20efisien%20dan%20efektif%20dalam%20meningkat
